## Commit Message Format (MANDATORY)

Every commit MUST follow the Odoo git guidelines ŌĆö use the `commit` skill (`/commit`), or follow its format:

```
[TAG] module_name: short description (< 50 chars)

WHY this change is needed (not WHAT ŌĆö the diff shows WHAT).

{{ ticket_prefix }}-XXX
```

Tags: `[FIX]`, `[IMP]`, `[ADD]`, `[REM]`, `[REF]`, `[PERF]`, `[CLN]`, etc.
Module name = technical name (e.g. `{{ module_prefix }}_project_software`).
Imperative mood. Task key in body. See `commit` skill for full reference.

