## Available Subagents

Defined in `.claude/agents/`:

| Agent | Purpose | Tools | Preloaded Skills |
|-------|---------|-------|-----------------|
| `dev` | Development ŌĆö writes code | All | style, code-patterns |
| `review` | QC + code review ŌĆö read-only analysis | Read, Grep, Glob, Bash | style, testing |

Interactive Odoo debugging is the **`debug` skill** (mcp-pdb), run in-context ŌĆö not a subagent.

## Collecting subagent returns

Every `dev` / `review` subagent returns a structured closing block:

    FILES_CHANGED: <list>
    OPEN_THREADS: <list, or "none">
    DECISIONS: <scope expansions or design calls, or "none">

Maintain running lists across ALL phases:

- `ALL_FILES_CHANGED` ŌĆö union of FILES_CHANGED from every `dev` spawn
- `ALL_OPEN_THREADS` ŌĆö every OPEN_THREAD returned, any phase
- `ALL_DECISIONS` ŌĆö every DECISION returned, any phase

These feed Phase 6 (Memory Closure). If a subagent forgets the closing block, ask it again ŌĆö do not guess.

