   The leading `/` in `--test-tags /<MODULE_NAME>` is mandatory ŌĆö a bare
   name selects a (nonexistent) TAG, runs 0 tests and goes false-green.
   Confirm the log reports a **non-zero test count** (`odoo.tests.result:
   ŌĆ” of N tests`).
3. Check for ERROR, CRITICAL, test failures, tracebacks.
4. Start this session's Odoo: `systemctl --user start odoo-wt@<slug>.service`
